tags.name: a11y-carousel
tags.description:
`a11y-carousel`
Layers images over each other with a slider interface to compare them

Events:

  * `selection-changed` {`CustomEvent<this>`} - Fires when selection update, so that parent radio group can listen for it.

Attributes:

  * `no-buttons` {`boolean`} - 

  * `no-prev-next` {`boolean`} - 

  * `prevLabel` {`string`} - 

  * `nextLabel` {`string`} - 

  * `itemData` {`any[]`} - 

  * `selection` {`string`} - 

Properties:

  * `first` - gets id for first figure

  * `prev` - gets id for previous figure

  * `last` - gets id for last figure

  * `next` - gets id for next figure

  * `noButtons` {`boolean`} - 

  * `noPrevNext` {`boolean`} - 

  * `prevLabel` {`string`} - 

  * `nextLabel` {`string`} - 

  * `itemData` {`any[]`} - 

  * `selection` {`string`} - 

  * `selectedIndex` {`number`} - index of selected item

  * `__observer` - mutation observer for tabs

  * `__allowNull` {`boolean`} - allows no item to be selected

  * `__query` {`string`} - overrides query selector for slotted children

  * `__selected` {`string`} - overrides attribute to apply to selected item

  * `__selectEvent` {`string`} - overrides name of event that selects item
